@Node Main "PBM.guide"

@{b}MP_PBM@{ub} 5.0 Contents
*******************

@Remark $VER: MP_PBM 5.0 (15.5.96)

MP_PBM provides a Gui interface to the PBM Plus graphics conversion
software. It lets you Load, Process and Save images. It shows a gui for
each program letting you input the program parameters.


 @{" Requirements      " Link "Requirements"}             Software and Hardware required

 @{" Cycle Gadget      " Link "Selection"}             Select the Mode
 @{" Load Gadget       " Link "Load"}             Select Load Format
 @{" Process Gadget    " Link "Process"}             Select Process
 @{" Misc Gadget       " Link "Misc"}             Select Misc Process
 @{" Save Gadget       " Link "Save"}             Select Save Format

 @{" History           " Link "History"}             Version History

 @{" Distribution      " Link "Distribution"}             Copyright and distribution requirements

 @{" Index             " Link "Index"}             The index for this guide


@EndNode

@Node "Requirements" "PBM.guide/Requirements"
@Next "Selection"
@Prev "Main"
@Toc "Main"

Software and Hardware required
******************************

OS3.0+ is required.


@EndNode

@Node "Selection" "PBM.guide/Selection"
@Next "Load"
@Prev "Requirements"
@Toc "Main"

Select the Mode
***************

This gadget selects the Mode. @{"Load" Link "Load"} an image, @{"Process" Link "Process"} an image, @{"Misc" Link "Misc"}
process an image, or @{"Save" Link "Save"} an image.

The @{b}M@{ub} key can be used to cycle this gadget.


@EndNode

@Node "Load" "PBM.guide/Load"
@Next "Process"
@Prev "Selection"
@Toc "Main"

Select Load Format
******************

This gadget can be used to select the load format. Click on @{b}Ok@{ub} to load
an image.

The @{b}L@{ub} key can be used to cycle this gadget.


@EndNode

@Node "Process" "PBM.guide/Process"
@Next "Misc"
@Prev "Load"
@Toc "Main"

Select Process
**************

This gadget can be used to select the Process mode. Click on @{b}Ok@{ub} to
process an image.

The @{b}P@{ub} key can be used to cycle this gadget.


@EndNode

@Node "Misc" "PBM.guide/Misc"
@Next "Save"
@Prev "Process"
@Toc "Main"

Select Misc Process
*******************

This gadget can be used to select the Misc Process mode. Click on @{b}Ok@{ub} to
process an image.

The @{b}I@{ub} key can be used to cycle this gadget.


@EndNode

@Node "Save" "PBM.guide/Save"
@Next "History"
@Prev "Misc"
@Toc "Main"

Select Save Format
******************

This gadget can be used to select the save format. Click on @{b}Ok@{ub} to save
an image.

The @{b}S@{ub} key can be used to cycle this gadget.


@EndNode

@Node "History" "PBM.guide/History"
@Next "Distribution"
@Prev "Save"
@Toc "Main"

